Ethical Hacker

Skills

We looking to add an extra talent to our team, it should be someone with experience at least two years in "Web Application Penetration Testing".

Necessary Knowledge: OWASP TOP 10; Code Skills; Experience with Static Code Analysis Tools (sonarqube, Checkmarx); Code Review - is a plus.

Certifications: OSWE - Offensive; OSCP - Offensive; CRTE - Pentester Academy; OSCE - Offensive; CRTP- Pentester Academy eWPTv1/eWPTv2 - elearn security.

Submit resumes at ana.m@tabella.cz
